videos.headline: Iowa cashes in on Northwestern fumble with TD
videos.description: Zach VanValkenburg recovers the Isaiah Bowser fumble, which leads to Tyler Goodson scoring the 15-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa cashes in on Northwestern fumble with TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern gets back in game with 2 second quarter rushing TDs
videos.description: After trailing 17-0, Northwestern gets touchdowns from Kyric McGowan and Jesse Brown to cut into the Iowa lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Northwestern gets back in game with 2 second quarter rushing TDs) 2020/10/31 ESHEET
